<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Avif on Ricard's code gists</title><link>https://ricard.dev/gists/tags/avif/</link><description>Recent content in Avif on Ricard's code gists</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ricard.dev/gists/tags/avif/atom.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Convert all JPG images to AVIF</title><link>https://ricard.dev/gists/2024-02-28/</link><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ricard.dev/gists/2024-02-28/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;It loops through all the jpg images in the folder and converts them to AVIF with the given configuration of quality and size.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It requires &lt;a href="https://github.com/AOMediaCodec/libavif"&gt;libavif&lt;/a&gt; to be installed on the machine. If you&amp;rsquo;re on MacOS &lt;a href="https://formulae.brew.sh/formula/libavif"&gt;grab it on Homebrew&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="background-color:#fff;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#0a3069"&gt;`&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#cf222e"&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; file in *.jpg&lt;span style="color:#1f2328"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#cf222e"&gt;do&lt;/span&gt; avifenc -q &lt;span style="color:#0550ae"&gt;50&lt;/span&gt; --speed &lt;span style="color:#0550ae"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt; --ignore-exif &lt;span style="color:#0a3069"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#953800"&gt;$file&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#0a3069"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; -o &lt;span style="color:#0a3069"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#0a3069"&gt;${&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#953800"&gt;file&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#1f2328"&gt;%.*&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#0a3069"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#0a3069"&gt;.avif&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#1f2328"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#cf222e"&gt;done&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#0a3069"&gt;`&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>